description: Experience all Southie has to offer at 68 Middle Street. Located just outside of Andrew Square, this well laid out and well cared for 1 bedroom condo gives you a great return on your investment with everything you could want like central AC and heating, granite counters, stainless appliances, crown molding, jetted tub, storage, laundry, private outdoor space, hardwood floors and more! With a $110/mo condo fee and under $1500 in annual taxes utilizing your exemption, this is the best bang for your buck. The hot water heater is less than 2 years old and the AC was replaced in July 2021. With the Red Line a moment away, this is a perfect home for a first time buyer, investor, or someone seeking a pied de terre. Pet friendly association welcomes fury friends to enjoy the yard. Come see for yourself!
